<ContentPage
  title="Fula Devi"
  description="Who Fula Devi was, the quiet ways she helped others, the dignity she preserved, and the teaching remembered by her family."
>
  <p>Fula Devi (1958–2006) lived in Bihar, India.</p>
  <p>
    She was the mother of the institution's co-founder and the wife of its
    first Secretary.
  </p>
  <p>She never founded an institution or sought public recognition.</p>
  <p>
    People who knew her remember the quiet kindness she showed through everyday
    acts of generosity and care.
  </p>

